data.description: Welcome to this delightful 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom home in the heart of Kansas City. Nestled in a prime location, this home embodies the charm and character that Kansas City is known for, while its modern updates ensure you have everything you need for contemporary living. With a bonus non-conforming 3rd bedroom, you'll have the space you need to accommodate your unique lifestyle. Updated kitchen with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances, make this home ideal for hosting friends and family. The spacious backyard offers an ideal spot to entertain outside and give your pets plenty of space to play! Enjoy the perfect mix of urban living and suburban tranquility while being within walking distance to Westport and a stone's throw from the renowned Country Club Plaza. This is your opportunity to own a piece of Kansas City's heart; don't miss out! Schedule a viewing today and experience the comfort and convenience of this exceptional home.
